Alias      Myanti-D0   anti-D0
Alias      MyD0        D0
ChargeConj MyD0        Myanti-D0
Alias myK_S0      K_S0
ChargeConj myK_S0 myK_S0
Alias My_rho0 rho0
ChargeConj My_rho0 My_rho0
#
Decay B0sig
  1.000        My_rho0     Myanti-D0              SVS;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B0sig
#
Decay MyD0
  1.000     myK_S0 pi+  pi-        PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-D0
#
Decay myK_S0
  1.000 pi+ pi-                     PHSP;
Enddecay
#
Decay My_rho0
  1.000 pi+ pi-                    VSS;
Enddecay
#
End
